{
  "id": "adv_bond_ngs_01_05",
  "title": "伊吹渚5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルスマイル……アイドル、スマイル……\nうーん……アイドル～、スマイル～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idol smile… Idol‚ smile…\nHmm… Idol~‚ smile~…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12633.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "……？　葵ちゃん、何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…? Aoi-chan‚ what are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.003243351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "いや……こころが「葵さんもたまには可愛さアピール\nした方がいいですよ、ギャップを狙いましょう」……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… it's just that Kokoro kept saying‚ \"Aoi-san‚ you should\nappeal with your cuteness sometimes‚ aim for the gap\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3666657765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "とか、あまりにも言うから\nちょっと試しにやってただけだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was so persistent about it‚\nso I was just giving it a try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.3640806517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "結局、よく分からないんだけどね。どうアピールすれば\nいいのか分からないし、僕に似合うのかも分からないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't really get it‚ though. I don't know how to\nappeal‚ or if it even suits me at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4307472707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんも、昔はよく悩んでたな～\n『可愛い』ってなんだろうって真剣に考えちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan used to worry about that a lot too~\nShe would seriously think about what \"cute\" really means.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7641031743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、練習するなら私も付き合うよ。琴乃ちゃんと\n一緒に、可愛いポーズの研究をしてたことがあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! If you're practicing‚ I'll join you. I used to\nstudy cute poses together with Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3895228864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、こころもよく研究してたっけ……\nまぁ、一度くらいは経験として、やってみようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Kokoro used to study them often too…\nWell‚ I guess I'll try it once‚ just for the experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5064841113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "井川葵だよー\n今日はみんなにハッピーをお届けだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Aoi Igawa~\nI'm here to deliver happiness to everyone today~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0502526762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……渚、さっきから言われた通りやってみてるけど\nやっぱり僕には似合わないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… Nagisa‚ I've been doing as you said‚\nbut it really doesn't suit me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2471868835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも他のアイドルがやってるなら\nわざわざ僕がやる必要も――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ if other idols are already doing it‚\nthere's no need for me to go out of my way to――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6605201406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "いいねいいね！　葵ちゃん、すっごく可愛い！\nやっぱりギャップだね、ギャップ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice‚ nice! Aoi-chan‚ you're so cute!\nIt's all about the gap‚ the gap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5938532514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、お世辞はいらないんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I don't need empty flattery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.684034761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　そのちょっと照れた顔も可愛い！\n写真を撮って、莉央さんに見せてあげたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! That slightly embarrassed face is cute too!\nI want to take a picture and show it to Rio-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1577535155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "こんなの見せたら、莉央はお腹を抱えて笑うと思うよ\nというか、別に照れてないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you show her this‚ Rio will probably double over laughing.\nAnyway‚ I'm not particularly embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9387965365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "笑いのツボが浅い人ってたまにいるけど\n渚の場合は、可愛いのツボが浅いのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Some people are easily amused and laugh at anything‚\nbut in your case‚ Nagisa‚ maybe your bar for \"cute\" is just low…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8753952825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、葵ちゃん！　次のポーズ！\nうんうん、じゃあ次！　からの～、次のポーズ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Aoi-chan! Next pose!\nMm-hmm‚ okay next! And then~ next pose!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2982977077,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13235.024435799985
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん、渚。急に踊りたくなってきたから\n公園にでも行ってくるよ。それじゃあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry‚ Nagisa. I suddenly feel like dancing‚\nso I'm going to the park for a bit. See ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1666545867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、待って！　ダンスなら、とびっきり可愛い\n振り付けのを教えてあげるから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ wait! If you're going to dance‚ I'll teach you\na super cute choreography…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4835498972,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9949.772246300001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_ngs_01_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ、せっかく盛り上がってきたとこなのに～！\n……絶対に逃がさないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez‚ things were just starting to get exciting~!\n…I'm definitely not letting you get away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.5421210768,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}